  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You have learned how to manipulate gravity around a living being: whenever a creature is affected by one of your spells, you can move the target 5 feet to an unoccupied space of your choice if the target is willing to move, the spell hits it with an attack, or it fails a saving throw against the spell.</p><p>If the creature is under the effects of your Adjust Density then you can move the target a number of feet equal to your Intelligence modifier (minimum of 1) to an unoccupied space of your choice.</p><p>A creature of Huge size or larger is only moved a maximum of 10 feet, unless the spell would already move it.</p>",
